Name: De Knijp
Review Text: Wonderful small bistro with great food and booze. Value. Best chicken soup I have had since childhood. Full of flavour. Chef knows his stuff.

Name: De Knijp
Review Text: We have been dining here for over 28 years and visit everytime we are in Amsterdam, which is at least 2-3 times a year.  The food has always been amazing.  I can highly reccommend the satay, seabass and teriyaki salmon.  The staff are very friendly and attentive.  You won't be disappointed.

Name: De Knijp
